<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 12:22:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>郑在法国公开赛上大获全胜，让科内特退役</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-sends-cornet-into-retirement-with-french-open-thumping-2024-05-28/</link><description>周二，七号种子郑沁文以6-2 6-1击败阿莉兹·科内特，进入法国网球公开赛第二轮，这位法国女单在连续20年在大满贯赛场上惨败，惨遭退役。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 12:07:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-sends-cornet-into-retirement-with-french-open-thumping-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>当美国迈向更快的股票结算时，其他国家在哪里？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-moves-towards-faster-stock-settlement-where-are-other-countries-2024-05-28/</link><description>美国证券交易委员会于 2023 年 2 月通过一项规则，从周二开始，将证券交易的结算周期从交易后的两个工作日缩短至一个工作日。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 11:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-moves-towards-faster-stock-settlement-where-are-other-countries-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>随着替代供应商的出现，美国对中国医疗进口产品的关税面临业界质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/us-tariffs-chinese-medical-imports-face-industry-doubt-alternative-suppliers-2024-05-28/</link><description>行业高管表示，美国对中国医用手套、注射器和口罩征收更高的关税不太可能使美国生产商更具竞争力，因为其他低成本供应商预计将涌入填补缺口。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 11:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/us-tariffs-chinese-medical-imports-face-industry-doubt-alternative-suppliers-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>台湾立法院通过有争议的改革法案，数千人抗议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-protest-taiwans-parliament-passes-contested-reforms-2024-05-28/</link><description>周二，台湾议会通过了一项旨在加强对政府监督的改革方案，该方案由反对派推动，但遭到执政党的反对，而执政党没有足够的人数来阻止该方案，数千人在议会外举行抗议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:34:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-protest-taiwans-parliament-passes-contested-reforms-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>英国高级立法者希望在 Shein 可能在伦敦上市之前对其进行更多审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/senior-uk-lawmakers-want-more-scrutiny-shein-ahead-possible-london-listing-2024-05-28/</link><description>英国资深立法者质疑快时尚巨头 Shein 是否适合在伦敦股市上市，并呼吁对这家中国创立的公司进行更严格的审查。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:14:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/senior-uk-lawmakers-want-more-scrutiny-shein-ahead-possible-london-listing-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：盘后华尔街继续高涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-28/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>香港根据新国安法逮捕六名煽动叛乱罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-police-arrest-six-people-under-new-national-security-law-2024-05-28/</link><description>香港国家安全警察周二根据一项新的安全法在全市逮捕了六人，罪名是涉嫌煽动叛乱，其中包括一名已经入狱的民主派大律师。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 09:39:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-police-arrest-six-people-under-new-national-security-law-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，苹果 4 月份 iPhone 在中国销量猛增 52%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-iphone-sales-april-jump-52-data-shows-2024-05-28/</link><description>中国政府下属的一家研究公司的数据显示，4 月份苹果在中国的智能手机出货量同比增长 52%，延续了 3 月份的反弹势头。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 08:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-iphone-sales-april-jump-52-data-shows-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>新冠疫情过后，中国重返非洲并加大矿产资源投入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/post-covid-china-is-back-africa-doubling-down-minerals-2024-05-28/</link><description>路透社对贷款、投资和贸易数据的分析显示，中国的旗舰经济合作计划在全球大流行期间的平静期后正在反弹，其中非洲是主要焦点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 06:05:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/post-covid-china-is-back-africa-doubling-down-minerals-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国呼吁停止红海袭击民用船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-calls-red-sea-attacks-civilian-ships-end-2024-05-28/</link><description>周二，中国外交部长王毅在北京会见也门外长时，中国呼吁停止对红海民用船只的袭击，并确保红海航行安全。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 05:22:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-calls-red-sea-attacks-civilian-ships-end-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统感谢紧急升空对抗中国演习的飞行员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-thanks-pilots-who-scrambled-against-china-drills-2024-05-28/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周二在听取有关前线空军基地事件的通报时，对上周在台湾绕岛军演期间与中国进行紧急升空的战斗机飞行员表示感谢。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 05:08:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-thanks-pilots-who-scrambled-against-china-drills-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>中美同意通过持续对话管控海上风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-agree-manage-maritime-risks-through-continued-dialogue-2024-05-28/</link><description>中国外交部周二表示，中美就海洋事务举行磋商，双方同意保持对话、管控风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 04:20:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-agree-manage-maritime-risks-through-continued-dialogue-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国驳斥手机入境检查的说法“荒谬”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dismisses-preposterous-claims-entry-checks-phones-2024-05-28/</link><description>当局周二表示，有关从 7 月 1 日起所有抵达中国的人都将接受手机检查的说法是错误的，并称其为“反华势力”歪曲事实。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 04:03:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dismisses-preposterous-claims-entry-checks-phones-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰银行将收购德国私人银行，这是自 2008 年金融危机以来最大的一笔交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/abn-amro-buy-german-lender-hauck-aufhuser-lampe-730-million-2024-05-28/</link><description>荷兰银行已同意以 6.72 亿欧元（7.3 亿美元）的价格从中国复星国际收购德国私人银行 Hauck Aufhäuser Lampe (HAL)，以扩大财富管理业务，这是自全球金融危机以来荷兰银行最大的一笔交易。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 03:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/abn-amro-buy-german-lender-hauck-aufhuser-lampe-730-million-2024-05-28/</guid></item><item><title>全球股市坚挺，交易员等待通胀数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-28/</link><description>周二，世界股市维持在历史高位附近，美国国债收益率小幅走低，因投资者等待本周晚些时候公布的大西洋两岸通胀数据。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 02:24:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>